1. **Navbar** → Home, Shop, Categories, About linkleri + Search + Cart + Sign In butonu
2. **Hero Section** → "Shop Now" + "View Collections" butonları + Trending Now glass kartı
3. **Featured Products** → 4 ürün kartı (mock veri, emoji görsel) + "View All" linki

